{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_06_01_short",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 きっと驚きますわよ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマス前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On a day before Christmas",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの単独ライブ……琴乃の誕生日……\nそしてクリスマスパーティー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest's solo live… Kotono-san's birthday…\nand the Christmas party…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今年のクリスマスは\n楽しいことが目白押しですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year's Christmas is\nfilled with exciting events!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "随分と嬉しそうだが\nクリスマスがそんなに楽しみなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem quite happy.\nAre you really looking forward to Christmas this much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "当然です！　今もクリスマスライブに向けて\n新曲を作っていますが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Right now‚ I'm working on a new song for\nthe Christmas live but……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで話し合い、曲がどんどん形になっていくのが\n楽しいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We discuss together‚ and the song is gradually\ntaking shape‚ which is enjoyable!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃に内緒で集まって\n誕生日のサプライズを計画するのも楽しいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ secretly gathering to plan a surprise for\nKotono-san's birthday is also fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスパーティーに向けて\nツリーや飾り付けを準備するのは楽しいですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparing the tree and decorations\nfor the Christmas party is exciting too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうで何よりだが、あまり浮かれ過ぎないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's great to see you excited‚ but don't get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "浮かれてなんかいませんわ\n私はいつだって冷静沈着ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not getting carried away.\nI'm always composed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そっちこそ、本音では私達のクリスマスパーティーに\n参加したいのではございませんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you the one who secretly wants to\njoin our Christmas party?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}